On your second point, so I anticipate changes.

745
00:39:37.506 --> 00:39:39.626
So if this is just codifying what's happened, two points.

746
00:39:40.086 --> 00:39:43.886
One, I don't think it is, and two, what's happening now is simply not

747
00:39:43.926 --> 00:39:46.486
acceptable. Your second point, sorry, remind me.

748
00:39:46.566 --> 00:39:49.856
Oh, just that the government's made a record investment, the biggest ever-

749
00:39:49.856 --> 00:39:50.426
Oh, yes. Yes

750
00:39:50.606 --> 00:39:50.856
... into disability support services.

751
00:39:50.856 --> 00:39:51.146
Of course.

752
00:39:51.186 --> 00:39:51.495
Why do you think it won't-

753
